special_powers.description: MOVE: Improved Movement: Characters. Move in a direct path. After resolutions, make a close attack targeting all opposing characters moved through, regardless of adjacency. Hit characters are dealt this character's printed damage instead of normal damage.

special_powers.name: ASGARDIANS OF THE GALAXY
special_powers.description: Valkyrie has Guardians team ability. // Friendly characters that can use Guardians team ability can use Defenders team ability.

special_powers.name: ARAGORN, CHARGE!
special_powers.description: Blades/Claws/Fangs, KNOCKBACK. // POWER: Move in a direct path, after resolutions make a close attack targeting an opposing character she moved through regardless of adjacency.

special_powers.name: REALM OF THE GIANTS: MUSPELHEIM
special_powers.description: If Surtur is 150 points or more, when an opposing character would reduce damage, they reduce that damage by one less. When Surtur is KO'd, this effect continues for the rest of the game.

special_powers.name: MARCH ON ASGARD
special_powers.description: FREE: If no characters have been placed this turn, place Surtur adjacent to an opposing character that attacked a friendly character since your last turn.

special_powers.name: THE ETERNAL FLAME
special_powers.description: Penetrating/Psychic Blast, Precision Strike, Energy Explosion.

special_powers.name: KING OF THE FIRE GIANTS
special_powers.description: STOP. Toughness.

special_powers.name: THE SWORD TWILIGHT
special_powers.description: When Surtur hits with a close attack, choose a standard defense power or STOP. Hit characters can't use the chosen power or ability until your next turn.

special_powers.name: REALM OF THE GIANTS: NIFLHEIM
special_powers.description: If Ymir is 150 points or more, opposing characters modify speed -1 and range -2. When this character is KO'd, this effect continues for the rest of the game.

special_powers.name: COLOSSAL RETALIATION: NUMBING COLD
special_powers.description: POWER: If no friendly character has been placed this turn, choose an opposing character that attacked Ymir or damaged a friendly character since your last turn. Place Ymir such that he can make a close attack targeting the chosen character then do so. A hit character modifies its combat values -1 for each action token on it until your next turn.

special_powers.name: FIMBULWINTER
special_powers.description: [3 bolts], Incapacitate. When Ymir uses Incapacitate, he still deals normal damage.

special_powers.name: KING OF THE ICE GIANTS
special_powers.description: STOP. Toughness.

special_powers.name: THE WINDS OF OBLIVION
special_powers.description: FREE: Make an attack, but only to target characters with action tokens.
